s.sites.mtu.edu/mhugl/2015/10/11/general-william-hull-draft/ |website=Michigan Tech |archive-url= |archive-date= |url-status= |access-date= |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite web |title=Arbitration, Mediation, and Conciliation \u2013 Jay's treaty and the treaty of ghent |url=http://www.americanforeignrelations.com/A-D/Arbitration-Mediation-and-Conciliation-Jay-s-treaty-and-the-treaty-of-ghent.html |website=Encyclopedia of the New American Nation |accessdate=July 1, 2013 |ref=CITEREFArbitration, Mediation, Conciliation}}\n* {{cite book |last=Army and Navy Journal Incorporated |title=The United States Army and Navy Journal and Gazette of the Regular and Volunteer Forces |volume=Vol. 3 |year=1865 |publisher=Princeton University |isbn= |location= |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Auchinleck |first=Gilbert |title=A History of the War Between Great Britain and the United States of America: During the Years 1812, 1813, and 1814 |date=1855 |url=https://archive.org/details/ahistorywarbetw00auchgoog |page=[https://archive.org/details/ahistorywarbetw00auchgoog/page/n63 49] |publisher=Maclear & Company |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Banner |first=James M. |title=To the Hartford Convention: The Federalists and the Origins of Party Politics in Massachusetts, 1789\u20131815 |url=https://archive.org/details/tohartfordconven0000bann |url-access=registration |year=1970 |location=New York |publisher=Knopf |isbn= |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite web |title=Battle of Mackinac Island, July 17, 1812 |url=http://www.historyofwar.org/articles/battles_mackinac_island_1812.html |website=HistoryofWar.org |access-date=May 23, 2017 |ref=CITEREFBattle of Mackinac}}\n* {{cite book |last=Benn |first=Carl |title=The War of 1812 |year=2002 |place=Oxford |publisher=[[Osprey Publishing]] |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=aG2ICwAAQBAJ |isbn=978-1-84176-466-5 |ref=harv}}\n* {{cite book |last=Benn |first=Carl |last2=Marston |first2=Daniel |title=Liberty or Death: Wars That Forged a Nation |year=2006 |place=Oxford |publishe